<i>Sophora tetraptera</i> var.: <i>grandiflora</i>; the Koromiko-taranga, <i>Veronica,</i> several species; the Mairehau, <i>Phebalium nudum</i>; the Toro, <i>Persoonia</i> Toro; the Pukapuka, <i>Brachyglottis repanda</i>; the Northern Maire,

